  "AFG:baghlan": "Northern province known for its sugar beet industry and the ancient Surkh Kotal site, a major Kushan-era fire temple excavated by French archaeologists.",
  "AFG:samangan": "Northern province home to Takht-i-Rustam, a remarkable 4th–5th century rock-cut Buddhist stupa monastery near the capital Aybak.",
  // AGO
