  "AGO:lunda sul": "Rich in alluvial diamonds; its capital Saurimo is the logistical centre for the southeastern diamond fields.",
  "AGO:cuanza sul": "A leading sugar-cane and agricultural province; its capital is Sumbe (formerly Novo Redondo) on the Atlantic coast.",
