  "AIA:sandy ground": "Anguilla's main working harbour at Road Bay, known as the island's nightlife hub with beach bars and restaurants along the salt pond.",
  "AIA:south hill": "A commercial district bisected by Anguilla's main road, home to a diverse mix of restaurants, shops, and the junction toward Meads Bay.",
