  // IOA
  "IOA:cocos": "The Cocos (Keeling) Islands are an Australian territory of 27 coral islands with a population of around 600, governed partly by an elected Shire Council.",
  "IOA:christmas island": "Christmas Island hosts a NASA tracking station and is known for the annual red crab migration of tens of millions of crabs to the sea.",
  // IOT
