  "IRN:east azerbaijan": "Capital Tabriz houses the historic Grand Bazaar, a UNESCO World Heritage Site and major trade hub since the Silk Road era.",
  "IRN:ardabil": "Contains the UNESCO-listed Sheikh Safi al-Din shrine complex, the ancestral home of the Safavid dynasty founded in the 16th century.",
