  "IRQ:erbil": "Capital of the Kurdistan Region; Erbil Citadel, continuously inhabited for over 6,000 years, is a UNESCO World Heritage Site.",
  "IRQ:basra": "Iraq's only major port province on the Persian Gulf, handling the vast majority of the country's crude oil exports.",
