  "UGA:hoima": "Capital of Uganda's Bunyoro Kingdom, now the administrative hub of the country's developing petroleum industry.",
  "UGA:ntoroko": "A remote district on Lake Albert's southern shore, bordering DRC and known for its fisheries and wildlife corridor.",
