  "UGA:kiboga": "A sparsely populated central district known for cattle ranching and as part of Uganda's traditional Buganda Kingdom.",
  "UGA:mpigi": "Borders Lake Victoria near Kampala and is known for its proximity to Mpigi forest reserve and trade with the capital.",
