  "UGA:butaleja": "A Bukedi district known for rice cultivation in wetland areas and as a growing agricultural zone near the Kenya border.",
  "UGA:kibuku": "A Bukedi district known for cotton and sunflower farming, carved from Pallisa and Butebo in the eastern Uganda plains.",
